Elizabeth Alda https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elizabeth_Alda 0 Elizabeth Alda (born August 20, 1960) is an American actress who appeared in two films, including The Four Seasons with her sister Beatrice, and the short-lived television version. She is the daughter of Alan and Arlene Alda.
